text: Öjsjömyrarna Nature Reserve () is a nature reserve in Jämtland County in Sweden. It is part of the EU-wide Natura 2000-network. Öjsjömyrarna Nature Reserve has been created to protect a number of different kinds of wetlands. Between 2010–2015, some of the wetlands were restored through the EU-funded LIFE Programme. ==References== Category:Nature reserves in Sweden Category:Natura 2000 in Sweden Category:Tourist attractions in Jämtland County Category:Geography of Jämtland County Category:Protected areas established in 1998 Category:1998 establishments in Sweden
